{
  "stem": "2581.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No questions asked, they would be punished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, maybe between the older people, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my father was an officer in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our customers were mostly Polish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had respect for that picture in the uniform that they saw in our house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was not afraid to walk in the evening, even though he always walked with a cane.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that he needed the cane, but it was safer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Jewish boys in town were not afraid of the Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, really not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't a fighter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jewish children were told not to fight, to stay out of the fight, stay out of the way, you know, because they were always right.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know that our customers were the police, the commissioner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would warn us of any trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like we saw Tevya-- Tevya, they would come to warn us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, the commissioner, if he tried on some uniform in our house, he would pull the curtains, so the priest wouldn't see him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because what would happen-- and this is not just exaggerate, this is a fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because on Sundays, our shop was open, and the people would work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some of the peasants that would come from the villages would leave their bicycles in our house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I watched these bicycles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when they came out from the church and they would come to our house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would tell my father the things that were said about the Jews, especially Easter time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from time to time, there were fights, that they came out and they would attack Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would get drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The bars were open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They would come up from the church.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
